{
  "stem": "11998.6",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And about two days later, the commandant came and took-- had his insignias ripped off and had a paper in his hand that was supposedly saying that it is an order from Himmler that he should destroy the camp, burn the camp, and kill everybody.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He says I'm going to give the camp over to the Americans.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I don't have food to-- to take you out, so I'm going to give you over to the Americans.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And two days later, sister camp that have prisoner-- Russian prisoners of war, two guys escaped from the camp.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Guards-- there were very few guards were left by that time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was already end of April.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And [DRINKS WATER] two of them escaped and went with a motorcycle, one of the Nazi's motorcycles.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they went out through the front, and they brought in-- we were surrounded by Americans already.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But this was inside of a dense forest, and they were not in a hurry to go in-- into-- get into mines, step on a mine, or get into booby trap.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was May the 2nd, of 19-- May the 2nd, 1945.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was in-- not far from Muhldorf am Inn, which is about 60 kilometers south of Munich, and-- or let's see.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was east of Munich.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was in the-- in the foothills of mountains already.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Beautiful place.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so we were-- they brought a personnel carrier and a tank with them and to liberate us.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they arrested the Nazis that were there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they were standing on the-- on the personnel carrier.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they were-- the-- the-- the Americans were shielding them from us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And you know, somebody killed a horse.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the prisoners went after that and went-- started cutting the meat.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
